    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Git_u90E8_u7F72"><a href="#Git_u90E8_u7F72" class="headerlink" title="Git部署"></a>Git部署</h3><p>Install hexo-deployer-git.</p>
<pre><code class="bash">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save
</code></pre>
<p>Edit settings.</p>
<pre><code class="bash">deploy:
  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git
  repo: &lt;repository url&gt;
</code></pre>
<h3 id="RSS_u5206_u4EAB"><a href="#RSS_u5206_u4EAB" class="headerlink" title="RSS分享"></a>RSS分享</h3><p>安装RSS插件：</p>
<pre><code class="bash">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save
</code></pre>
<p>启用插件：<br>在hexo_config.yml文件添加插件配置项</p>
<pre><code class="bash">plugins:
- hexo-generator-feed
</code></pre>
<p>升级插件：</p>
<pre><code class="bash">npm update
</code></pre>
<p>卸载插件：</p>
<pre><code class="bash">npm uninstall hexo-generator-feed
</code></pre>
]]></content>
