    <link href="http://eloki.github.io/2016/01/01/Git-for-Windows%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/"/>
    <id>http://eloki.github.io/2016/01/01/Git-for-Windows安装与使用/</id>
    <published>2016-01-01T14:58:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-01-06T15:23:07.332Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>系统环境<br>Windows 10 专业版</p>
<h3 id="u4E0B_u8F7D_u5B89_u88C5"><a href="#u4E0B_u8F7D_u5B89_u88C5" class="headerlink" title="下载安装"></a>下载安装</h3><p><a href="https://git-for-windows.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://git-for-windows.github.io/</a></p>
<h3 id="u73AF_u5883_u53D8_u91CF"><a href="#u73AF_u5883_u53D8_u91CF" class="headerlink" title="环境变量"></a>环境变量</h3><pre><code class="bash">C:\Program Files\Git\cmd;
C:\Program Files\Git\mingw64\bin;C:\Program Files\Git\usr\bin;
</code></pre>
<h3 id="u7533_u8BF7Github_u8D26_u53F7"><a href="#u7533_u8BF7Github_u8D26_u53F7" class="headerlink" title="申请Github账号"></a>申请Github账号</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/</a></p>
<h3 id="u8BBE_u7F6EGit_u7684username_u548Cemail"><a href="#u8BBE_u7F6EGit_u7684username_u548Cemail" class="headerlink" title="设置Git的username和email"></a>设置Git的username和email</h3><pre><code class="bash">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"username"</span>
$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"name@org.com"</span>
$ git config --list
</code></pre>
<h3 id="u751F_u6210_u5BC6_u94A5"><a href="#u751F_u6210_u5BC6_u94A5" class="headerlink" title="生成密钥"></a>生成密钥</h3><pre><code class="bash">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"name@org.com"</span>
</code></pre>
<h2 id="Github_u6DFB_u52A0ssh_key"><a href="#Github_u6DFB_u52A0ssh_key" class="headerlink" title="Github添加ssh key"></a>Github添加ssh key</h2><p>Account Settings -&gt; SSH Keys -&gt; Add SSH key</p>
<h2 id="u9A8C_u8BC1ssh_key"><a href="#u9A8C_u8BC1ssh_key" class="headerlink" title="验证ssh key"></a>验证ssh key</h2><pre><code class="bash">$ ssh -T git@github.com
</code></pre>
]]></content>
